# Folders/modules
----------------
## grafanamcp
(Grafana's) GrafanaMCP (aka mpc-grafana) server/api, is for MCP's LLM prompting hookups
- a package sitting in front of Grafana server, exposing MCP-tooling to LLMs
- provides interfacing via AI editor programs like Zed.

## loki
(Grafana's) Loki is for the MCP logging resource.
- Loki is Grafana's logging solution, gets and saves logs (via promtail) from some some log-emitting source and puts into grafana server.
- Also allows LogQL fromatted queries in grafana dashboards.

## prometheus
(Grafana's) Prometheus is for the MCP metrics resource.
- Prometheus is the Grafana Metrics solution, scrapes metrics from some metrics-emitting source and puts into grafana server.
- Also allows PromQL fromatted queries in grafana dashboards.
